description: Cooking and trying to entertain your guests can be very stressful.  We provide everything you need in order for you to enjoy your guests and delicious food.  Several meal options are available based on the theme of your party.  We've catered many military events ranging from 10-150.  Business lunches, ceremonies, wine tastings, etc. we can do it all for you. Check us out!
name: Over the Plate
